#### ç”¨é€”3: å¤šé‡ç¶™æ‰¿ã§MROã«å¾“ã£ã¦å‘¼ã¶

```python
class A:
    def method(self):
        print("A")

class B(A):
    def method(self):
        print("B")
        super().method()  # MROã«å¾“ã£ã¦Aã‚’å‘¼ã¶

class C(A):
    def method(self):
        print("C")
        super().method()

