# å‡ºåŠ›:
# D
# B
# C
# A
```

### âš ï¸ super()ã®æ³¨æ„ç‚¹

#### æ³¨æ„1: super().__init__()ã‚’å¿˜ã‚Œã‚‹

```python
class Parent:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

class Child(Parent):
    def __init__(self, age):
        # super().__init__()ã‚’å¿˜ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹
        self.age = age

